node.text: We go driftin' in there, Bois!
We go driftin' in there, Bois!
@v.w.leon the ground definitely looks flat. This was done for the pure purpose of art I believe .
@ftro.fns nobody does it for art, there are a lot of factors that can affect the making of a road plus it is difficult to tell the angle of the road because how it is recorded
@ftro.fns the ground doesn't look level at all and yes it isn't
Why couldn’t they just connect the roads in a line The twisty road is pointless
@freakysaladtree its going up a mountain and a straight road would be too steep for the car
Why would someone build a road like this?
Abe sidha rod bna lo laudo kya jarurat hai itna ghuma fhira ke jane ki
Toyota Supra + phonk = drift on that fucking road
